name: Ohne Ordnung kein Brot - unordnung bringt Hungersnot! LCCN2004665836 - from Commons

desc.html: English:  Title: Ohne Ordnung kein Brot -- unordnung bringt Hungersnot! Abstract: Poster declares that without order there is no bread, that disorder brings starvation. A quote by Andrew Bonar Law, Leader of the British House of Commons, is included. Poster sponsored by the German Armistice Commission. Physical description: 1 print (poster) : lithograph, color ; 64 x 94 cm. Notes: Forms part of: Rehse-Archiv für Zeitgeschichte und Publizistik.; Bernhard.; Title from item.
